{
  "stem": "23090.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So yes, I, I was very much part of the, the process of viewing everything that was going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a time where someone was trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a group of guys, they were-- they were calling themselves the, the, the underground.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Some of them would call themselves for the Haganah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some would call themselves for the-- after the Russians, the Russian underground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know, it was to be a, a, a term that the young-- the younger guys would align with-- is, is that there were-- they wanted to fight, and so on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they caught these guys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a group of them, and took them right out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was about six or seven of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They hung them right on the, on the marktplatz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this German, who was the head of the ghetto, his name was Biebow, supposedly a relative to Himmler and one of the higher ranking people in the, in the, in the, in the Reich.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was in charge of the ghetto, and he was-- he was quite a shrewd individual and ran it like a-- like a precision instrument.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And had two personalities, obviously.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was able to retain or maintain order and somehow prevent a what we would call an uprising, as, as, as had happened in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he had a way about him, where he would delegate-- like we had the oldest Jew, which was Chaim Rumkowski.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He made him represent all the people, and they had hospitals, and they had their own police, and they had their own kitchens.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he says here, you run yourself, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But when the knife had to be used, he was the-- it was precision, this guy.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
